title: Sibling Advicery: Step Up Your P*ssy/What Are We?
description:
This week on Sibling Advicery, Monét and Bob contemplate if getting a Master's degree is worth it, offer suggestions on how to level up in the drag scene if you're feeling left behind, and give tips on how to make black friends. Tune in for LOTS of relationship help and so much more!!
